  "Description": {
    "English": "This experimental drive augments conventional <span class=\"name name-technology\">hyperdrive</span> technology by distorting local geometry at the point of warp initialisation, boosting <span class=\"name name-stellar\">range</span> and <span class=\"name name-stellar\">efficiency</span> far beyond standard drives.<br><br>User is advised to access Hyperdrive systems through the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Galactic Map</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "这种试作型驱动器能够在跃迁初始化阶段扭曲所在空间的几何结构，并大副提高传统<span class=\"name name-technology\">超光速推进器</span>科技的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">范围</span>以及<span class=\"name name-stellar\">效率</span>。<br><br>建议通过<span class=\"name name-stellar\">银河星图</span>操作超光速推进器系统。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一款實驗性十足的驅動器，藉扭曲空間跳躍起始時間點的局部幾何結構，增強一般<span class=\"name name-technology\">超空間驅動器</span>科技的威力，其<span class=\"name name-stellar\">距離</span>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">效率</span>遠超過標準驅動器。<br><br>建議使用者透過<span class=\"name name-stellar\">銀河地圖</span>存取超空間驅動器系統。"
  },
